Ondo Governor and Chairman of the Southwest Governors Forum Oluwarotimi Akeredolu has urged leaders of the All Progressives Congress(APC) to ensure the Presidency moves to the South for it to win the 2023 general elections. Akeredolu, who is Chairman of Security and Compliance for the party’s special convention, said the APC must be ready to rotate power to retain power,   2021/2022 UEFA Champions league team     My relationship with Hushpuppi, by Abba Kyari     Man uses old copies of The Nation for creative photoshoot   This was contained in a message posted on his verified Facebook page. The message reads: “APC must work to retain power. We must rotate power to retain power !!! Rotate to the South. Shikena.”